         Why all the confusion?  I have both items and have been using them for quite a while.  You get 20% more healing when you have EE III with BoD/Vex.  You get 20% more damage when you have EA III item.  Yes I have counted ticks.  Not with Vex, but I did with BoD when I got the items.  It works out that it lasts 11 ticks (66 seconds), compared to 9 ticks (54 seconds) without.</P><P><b><font color=blue>Retrievil Hesevil</font id=blue></b><BR><font color=red><b>58 DE Necromancer - Tallon Zek</font id=red></b><BR><font color=blue><b>56 Iksar Necromancer - Rodcet Nife</b></font id=blue><BR><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=333155" target="_blank">http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=333155</a><a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
