        <hr noshade size="2" color="#545A7D">
        
         The recourses are now flagged as necromancer level 127 spell (which translates to "not a necromancer spell") which sort of makes sense in that you can't directly cast the recourse.</P><P>However you would need a focus item that works on up to level 127 spells (like jboots click effect) in order to focus the recourse.</P><P>-Arbaon, Warlock, Luclin Server<a href="#top"><img src="icon_go_up.gif" height="15" width="15" border="0" align="right" alt="Go to Top of Page"></a></font></td>
